snippet.title: Tomb Raider II Trailer 1998
snippet.description:
Tomb Raider II Trailer 1998

Official Content From Eidos Interactive

The dazzling virtual sexbomb and action superstar Lara Croft returns in the mega-sequel to the groundbreaking, blockbuster hit! Join her in thrilling adventures. Named 'action game of the year!' - Electronic Gaming Monthly.
Platforms: Sony PlayStation
